message.body: Hey, you doing anything today?
Ah...nevermind.
Nope. Just bumming.
Hmm. Ok. We'll if anything changes, let me know.
I need to drop stuff off at Neumann Goretti, but they're apparently closed for the day.
Was gonna ask if you wanted to come.
But seems like I'll be going tomorrow now.
Oh man. I'm the wrong person to ask to go there. That's the last place I want to be. I haven't been there since graduation.
I've been there maybe once.
Are you on track with packing?
Uh. I'm pretty much done except for 1 or 2 more boxes.
I need to break my desk down Tuesday night.
Do you know what time you're leaving on Wednesday? Michael's gonna be at my house so I'll get to see you before you go.
I'm thinking the morning...they open at 7AM.
I don't think I'll be that early.
Maybe 8 or 9?
That's a good time. Oh. I got my start date today. I start next Tuesday and then get all of the details for my orientation schedule. So we're starting ne
w jobs a day apart!
That's funny. You excited?
Yeah. I'm nervous too. I thought I would have more time to brush up on nursing stuff. But the earlier I start the better.
Yeah, you can pick it up on the job.
Yup. Good luck with packing! See you later :)
